data.description: Introducing a charming 3-bed, 2-bath home in a beautiful master-planned community. You'll be greeted by an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living & dining areas. The home is flooded with natural light, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, making meal prep a breeze. The master bedroom includes an en-suite bathroom & walk-in closet for privacy & convenience. Step out onto the patio & be captivated by the water & sunset views. This backyard is stunning. The neighborhood boasts a variety of amenities, including a community pool, lazy river, sand volleyball, basketball, mini golf, fitness center, playgrounds, & dog park! Walking distance to Mayfield Elementary & new resort-style pool coming 2024. Located near Lake Lavon, & about 20 minutes from shopping & dining in Downtown McKinney or Allen Outlets.
